com.commander4j.db

Class JDBMenus

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.commander4j.db.JDBMenus

  • public class JDBMenus
extends java.lang.Object
    JDBMenus class is used to insert/update/delete records from the SYS_MENUS table. This table represents the structure of the menu's within the application.
